<TITLE> SIM card re-registration deadline widens to Dec 16 </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, Oct 9 (bdnews24.com)  The Bangladesh Telecommunication Regulatory Commission has extended the deadline for re-registration of SIM cards by two months to Dec 16, an official said Tuesday. The extension came on request from mobile phone companies who feared that the work might not be done by Oct 16, the original deadline, the official with BTRC added. bdnews2
